<p itemprop="description">一直想买个云台放家里，正好办携号转网电信送一个，那就不管效果，上就完事儿。</p><p itemprop="description">其实拿之前专门京东，值得买都看了测评。奈何确实这品牌产品有点小众都是简单的开箱介绍或者软文，心理还是挺忐忑的。</p><p itemprop="description">上图。﻿</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="荣耀亲选华为hilink智能云台简开箱" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd37b1c8e8237.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="荣耀亲选华为hilink智能云台简开箱" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd37e410c9114.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd385d8495916.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="所有配件。吐槽一下这个电源真的没什么设计，又大。就不能做小点，质感做好点吗。"/></a>所有配件。吐槽一下这个电源真的没什么设计，又大。就不能做小点，质感做好点吗。</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd781766a2019.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="看看这做工，这缝隙。"/></a>看看这做工，这缝隙。</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd96debf8958.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="大小对比。"/></a>大小对比。</span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="荣耀亲选华为hilink智能云台简开箱" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd9717f881784.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd974485a2394.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="背后这是音响"/></a>背后这是音响</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5eeq95/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/09/5f7fcd97791923138.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="可上墙"/></a>可上墙</span></p><p i